Bacterial 16S rRNA abundance

Results of qPCR for rRNA16S gene. Error bars show SEM. Efficiency = 100.2%, \(R^{2} = 0.99\).

16S rRNA gene abundance did differ significantly between elevations (F-test, \(p=0.072\)).

Results of qPCR for nosZ gene. Error bars show SEM. Efficiency = 78.4%, \(R^{2} = 0.99\).

nosZ gene abundance varied between elevations (F-test, \(p=<0.01\)).

Results of qPCR for narG gene. Error bars show SEM. Efficiency = 85.3%, \(R^{2} = 0.99\).

narG gene abundance did not vary significantly between elevations (F-test, \(p=0.131\)).

Results of qPCR for nirK gene. Error bars show SEM. Efficiency = 70.0%, \(R^{2} = 0.99\).

nirK gene abundance did not vary significantly between elevations (F-test, \(p=0.131\)).

Results of qPCR for nrfA gene. Error bars show SEM. Efficiency = 63.4%, \(R^{2} = 0.99\).

nrfA gene abundance varied significantly between elevations (F-test, \(p=<0.05\)).
